Personal Information Form
Overview

This project is a Personal Information Form built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The form collects essential user details such as name, mobile number, email, date of birth, gender, city, languages known, address, and allows users to upload a resume and a photo.

The form includes client-side validation and displays a confirmation alert upon successful submission.

