How to Use

Clone or download the project files.

Open index.html in any web browser.

Fill in the required fields marked with *.

Upload a PDF resume (mandatory) and an optional photo (JPG/PNG).

Click Submit Form.

A confirmation alert will appear, and the form will reset.

Customization

â• Add more cities or languages by editing the <select> and checkbox inputs in index.html.

